title: Jeff Goldblum Cancelled for Islam Comments?! | Ep 13
description: Do you think the allegations against Biden will ever catch up with him? And what tactics do you think the Democrats may use to silence his accuser? We go to Larry King for the answers! Also, Jeff Goldblum’s hate-mongering or totally reasonable question; a COVID-19 update showing the numbers aren’t adding up; our new sponsor: clock radios; and we conclude with “Stories from Papa Crowder."
